claude-plugin-discord
======================

This product is a modified derivative work based on the Discord plugin
from the "claude-plugins-official" project by Anthropic:

    https://github.com/anthropics/claude-plugins-official

The upstream project is licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.
A copy of the license is included in this repository as LICENSE.

Modifications in this fork (on top of upstream v0.0.4):

  1. Patch for issue #1091 — fix DM recipientId corruption after
     permission prompts.
     https://github.com/anthropics/claude-plugins-official/issues/1091

  2. Slash command support — adds registration and handling of Discord
     application (slash) commands via a commands.json config file.

  3. Additional tools and ergonomics (status_message, typing indicator
     adjustments, auto-transcription of inbound audio attachments, etc.).

